---
description: Apply naming conventions. Use when creating files, classes, or modules.
globs: src/**/*, tests/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---

Naming:
- Use descriptive, intention-revealing names
- No abbreviations except common ones (id, url, etc.)
- Verbs for actions, nouns for values
- Prefix booleans: `is`, `has`, `should`, `can`

File Naming:
- Source: `src/`
- Tests: `tests/` mirroring `src/` structure
